    <title>怎么样杀死自己</title>
    <link href="https://octopus862.github.io/2023/02/19/%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E6%A0%B7%E6%9D%80%E6%AD%BB%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/"/>
    <id>https://octopus862.github.io/2023/02/19/%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E6%A0%B7%E6%9D%80%E6%AD%BB%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/</id>
    <published>2023-02-19T02:55:45.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-03-11T12:06:43.884Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <strong><span class='p center logo large'>如何杀死自己</span></strong></p><h2 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a><span class='p center logo'>现实理论 精神痛苦 建立自信</span></h2><p> <strong><span class='p center logo'>Realistic theory mental pain building self-confidence</span></strong></p><div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 80%;"><iframe src="http://[240e:947:4001:0:3::3f9]/txmov2.a.kwimgs.com/upic/2023/02/19/11/BMjAyMzAyMTkxMTI1MzRfMTI2MjIyNzA0MV85NjU1NzMyMDkxNF8wXzM=_b_B998a943271d75b254b33d693b49cf84a.mp4?tag=1-1676777680-sr-0-taronrfjzf-dadcd77c22f3c7cb&clientCacheKey=3x5pyfru5h85s96_b.mp4&tt=b&di=5146f5ea&bp=10001&ali_redirect_ex_hot=66666810&ali_redirect_ex_beacon=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true" style="position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0; top: 0;"> </iframe></div><p> <strong><span class='p center logo large'>站长个人解读时间</span></strong><br>1、人的精力有限，行动力有限，所以一次只做一件事，只规划一件事。不要用愿景蛊惑自己，而要切实做到某件事。</p><p>2、既然如此，就必须把有限的精力用在刀刃上，用在关键事件上，比如早起、晚走ab老师竞争法和闪回。这些事情你做得别人做不得，成就感拉满，爽。</p><p>3、要有ddl（截止时间），否则就会无限拖延，最好是一周验收一次，保证自己能坚持下来的同时，收获成就感，自我肯定以坚持下去。</p><p>4、要有难度梯度，上来就地狱难度那活该白给。循序渐进，不要贪多，不要过分高估自己。</p><h2 id="-1"><a href="#-1" class="headerlink" title=""></a><psw>视频转载：https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Xv4y167WD?t=563.4</psw></h2>]]></content>
    
    
